    title:       'Pre-Washing Fabric: Do You Really Need To? (Custom Pattern Edition)',
    description: 'Find out why pre-washing fabric matters for custom sewing patterns. Learn which fabrics shrink, how to pre-wash properly, and when you can skip it.',
